00:06:03,569 --> 00:06:04,169
Berkahwin?

99
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:06,238
♪Bunga yang mekar mempesonakan♪

100
00:06:06,289 --> 00:06:07,768
Kenapa begitu cepat?

101
00:06:08,009 --> 00:06:10,248
Bukankah awak perlu meminang dahulu?

102
00:06:10,449 --> 00:06:10,768
Ya.

103
