Ya.

718
00:36:43,848 --> 00:36:45,489
Sila hantar Cik Song balik
ke kediamannya.

719
00:36:46,688 --> 00:36:48,329
Masa sudah lewat
dan dia berseorangan lagi.

720
00:36:48,848 --> 00:36:49,168
Ya.

721
00:36:49,729 --> 00:36:50,329
Zhuo Wenyuan.

722
00:36:56,688 --> 00:36:57,489
Ikut tuan awak.

723
