Qilang, rupanya
sesetengah barang di sini

757
00:38:46,289 --> 00:38:47,608
sudah dipindah keluar.

758
00:38:52,529 --> 00:38:53,368
Masuk ke dalam lagi.

759
00:38:53,848 --> 00:38:54,208
Baiklah.

760
00:38:57,089 --> 00:38:57,608
Jangan bergerak.

761
00:39:09,608 --> 00:39:10,009
Bukalah.

762
00:39:26,888 --> 00:39:28,928
Mungkin inilah tumbuhan Xizhao.

763
00:39:29,529 --> 00:39:30,848
Saya tak pernah jumpanya
di dalam Bianjing.

764
00:39:31,289 --> 00:39:32,608
Mungkin serbuk yang meracuni Sang Qi

765
00:39:32,608 --> 00:39:34,249
